message.name: ERR_XRV_EXTPARTY_STARTDATE_LATER_THAN_OFFICE_STARTDATE
message.locale: The Registration Date of an external party must not be later than the Start Date of any of its related external party offices.

message.name: ERR_XRV_EXTPARTY_ENDDATE_EARLIER_THAN_OFFICE_ENDDATE
message.locale: The End Date of an external party must not be earlier than the End Date of any of its related external party offices.
